ish in third place.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Footer Olympic Champions Track Tandem Men}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Chaillot, Louis}}\n[[Category:1914 births]]\n[[Category:1998 deaths]]\n[[Category:French male cyclists]]\n[[Category:Olympic cyclists of France]]\n[[Category:Olympic gold medalists for France]]\n[[Category:Olympic silver medalists for France]]\n[[Category:Olympic bronze medalists for France]]\n[[Category:Cyclists at the 1932 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Cyclists at the 1936 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Olympic medalists in cycling]]\n[[Category:People from Chaumont, Haute-Marne]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 1932 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 1936 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:French track cyclists]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Haute-Marne]]\n\n\n{{France-cycling-bio-1910s-stub}}\n{{France-cycling-Olympic-medalist-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{use dmy dates|date=July 2014}}\n{{Infobox cyclist\n| name           = Arne Berg\n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = \n| nickname       = \n| birth_date     = {{Birth date|1914|3|2|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = [[Chaumont, Haute-Marne|Chaumont]], [[France]]\n| death_date     = {{death date and age|1998|1|28|1914|3|2|df=yes}}\n| death_place    = [[Aubenas]], France\n| height         = \n| weight         = \n| currentteam    = \n| discipline     = \n| role           = \n| ridertype      = \n| amateuryears1  = \n| amateurteam1   = \n| proyears1      = \n| proteam1       = \n| majorwins      = \n| medaltemplates = \n{{MedalCountry | {{flag|FRA}} }}\n{{MedalSport|Men's [[cycling (sport)|cycling]]}}\n{{MedalCompetition|[[Olympic Games]]}}\n{{MedalGold | [[1932 Summer Olympics|1932 Los Angeles]] | [[Cycling at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tandem|Tandem]]}}\n{{MedalSilver | 1932 Los Angeles | [[Cycling at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's sprint|Individual sprint]]}}\n{{MedalBronze | [[1936 Summer Olympics|1936 Berlin]] | [[Cycling at the 1936 Summer Olympics \u2013 